<a href="#recipe-video" data-recipe="12809" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump-video wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-video-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-video-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-video-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path fill="#ffffff" d="M22,8H2C1.448,8,1,8.447,1,9v14c0,0.553,0.448,1,1,1h20c0.552,0,1-0.447,1-1V9C23,8.447,22.552,8,22,8z M9,20v-8l7,4L9,20z"></path> <rect data-color="color-2" x="0.001" y="2.111" transform="matrix(0.9798 -0.1999 0.1999 0.9798 -0.4028 2.2323)" width="21.701" height="2"></rect></g></svg></span> Jump to Video</a>
<a href="https://www.castironketo.net/wprm_print/keto-spanakopita" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-print wprm-recipe-link wprm-print-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-print-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent" data-recipe-id="12809" data-template="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-print-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="16px" height="16px" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g ><path fill="#ffffff" d="M19,5.09V1c0-0.552-0.448-1-1-1H6C5.448,0,5,0.448,5,1v4.09C2.167,5.569,0,8.033,0,11v7c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h4v4c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h12c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-4h4c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-7C24,8.033,21.833,5.569,19,5.09z M7,2h10v3H7V2z M17,22H7v-9h10V22z M18,10c-0.552,0-1-0.448-1-1c0-0.552,0.448-1,1-1s1,0.448,1,1C19,9.552,18.552,10,18,10z"/></g></svg></span> Print Recipe</a></div><p>This <strong>Keto Spanakopita</strong> recipe is our keto twist on the classic dish. It features fluffy phyllo bread, savory spinach, and creamy feta cheese. It's a low-carb, gluten-free recipe, perfect for meal prepping.</p>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_735f7e-d4 size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="801" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4.webp" alt="Low carb Spanakopita recipe ready to be served." class="kb-img wp-image-13246" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-360x240.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-768x513.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-720x481.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-180x120.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-150x100.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

