<h2 id="preparation-and-cooking-overview"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_48ebb6-49 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_48ebb6-49">Preparation and cooking overview</h2>

<p class="kt-adv-heading12803_4cc881-12 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_4cc881-12">Preparing this <strong>Spanakopita</strong> (<strong>Greek Spinach Pie)</strong> is super easy. Simply whisk the ingredients for phyllo dough, cook the phyllo sheets, and prepare the spinach filling. Then, layer the phyllo sheets with the filling, brush with butter, and bake for 20-25 minutes. You will have this Greek masterpiece on your dining table in one and a half hours.</p>


