<h2 id="how-to-make-keto-spanakopita-step-by-step-guide"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_4916cc-fe wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_4916cc-fe">How to make Keto Spanakopita: step-by-step guide</h2>

<h2 id="cooking-methods"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_6a4cc9-03 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_6a4cc9-03">Cooking methods</h2>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_98bd01-14 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_d96571-f1"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkSquare kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Baking</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_0bfcc0-8b"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkSquare kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Double-broiling</span></li></ul></div>


<h2 id="preparation-steps"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_493e41-9e wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_493e41-9e">Preparation steps</h2>


<ol>
<li>Gather all the ingredients.</li>



<li>Separate the whites from the yolks.</li>



<li>Thaw the frozen spinach and squeeze out any excess moisture.</li>



<li>Chop the spring onions.</li>



<li>Crumble the feta cheese.</li>



<li>Melt the butter in a small bowl and keep it aside.</li>
</ol>


<h2 id="cooking-instructions"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_c8c52b-ed wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_c8c52b-ed">Cooking instructions</h2>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_42f3e6-ae wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_42f3e6-ae">Make the phyllo batter</h3>


<ol>
<li>In a medium bowl, whisk the egg whites and water until foamy.</li>



<li>Add the melted butter, xanthan gum, and coconut flour to the bowl.</li>



<li>Mix everything until well combined.</li>
</ol>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_8a09b1-a1 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1.webp" alt="Ingredients and equipments made ready to prepare phyllo batter." class="kb-img wp-image-13255" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_a11290-98 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1.webp" alt="Mixing the ingredients together to prepare phyllo batter." class="kb-img wp-image-13256" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-4-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_7252fd-44 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_7252fd-44">Make the spinach mixture</h3>


<ol>
<li>Combine the raw spinach, chopped spring onions, egg yolk, crumbled feta cheese, and the aromatics in a large bowl.</li>



<li>Blend the ingredients thoroughly until they are well mixed.</li>
</ol>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_6cd9ed-ec size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1.webp" alt="Preparation process of Spanakopita recipe." class="kb-img wp-image-13253" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_249e8e-3f size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1.webp" alt="Mixing raw spinach, chopped spring onions, egg yolk, crumbled feta cheese, and the aromatics in a large bowl." class="kb-img wp-image-13254" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-2-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_c4c266-46 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_c4c266-46">Whip up the phyllo sheets</h3>


<ol>
<li>Prepare a double boiling set: Fill a pot with water and bring it to a boil. Then, place a pan on top of it.</li>



<li>Lightly grease the pan with cooking spray for the first phyllo. Pour approximately 3 tablespoons of phyllo batter into the pan.</li>



<li>Shake the pan to spread the mixture evenly and cook for about 3-4 minutes, until the edges separate from the pan.</li>



<li>Carefully remove the cooked phyllo and set it on a wire rack.</li>



<li>Repeat the process with the remaining batter.</li>
</ol>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_e85dd6-27 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1.webp" alt="Pouring phyllo batter to the pan." class="kb-img wp-image-13257" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-5-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_0f6427-c7 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1.webp" alt="Carefully removing the cooked phyllo sheet from a pan." class="kb-img wp-image-13258" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_93c34e-46 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_93c34e-46">Assemble the pie</h3>


<ol>
<li>On a baking dish, lay one phyllo sheet and brush it with melted butter. Continue to stack and brush each phyllo sheet until you have a total of 4-6 layers.</li>



<li>Next, spread the cooked spinach filling evenly on top of the sheets.</li>



<li>Repeat the layering process with the remaining phyllo sheets.</li>



<li>Then, cut the assembled pie into squares and pour the remaining melted butter over it.</li>
</ol>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_3f7f10-2c size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1.webp" alt="Applying butter to the surface of a baking dish." class="kb-img wp-image-13259" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-7-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_7edd7f-5c size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1.webp" alt="Stacking phyllo sheets on a baking dish." class="kb-img wp-image-13260" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_72b5b7-a5 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1.webp" alt="Spreading the cooked spinach filling evenly on top of phyllo sheets." class="kb-img wp-image-13261" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_5f3b5f-2f size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10.webp" alt="Cutting the assembled pie on the baking dish." class="kb-img wp-image-13262" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-10-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_f611d2-81 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11.webp" alt="Brushing the top of the pie with melted butter." class="kb-img wp-image-13263" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-11-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_d38cac-13 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12.webp" alt="Sprinkling sesame seeds on top of the pie." class="kb-img wp-image-13264" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-12-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_ecd4f6-2f wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_ecd4f6-2f">Bake the spanakopita</h3>


<ol>
<li>Preheat your oven to 355°F (180°C).</li>



<li>Transfer the baking dish to it and bake for 20-25 minutes, until the phyllo is golden and crispy.</li>



<li>Once done, remove it from the oven and let it cool off before serving.</li>
</ol>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_6f9869-73 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13.webp" alt="Serving a slice of Spanakopita from baking dish." class="kb-img wp-image-13265" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-360x203.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-720x405.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-480x270.webp 480w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-180x101.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-13-150x84.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_83c8b6-8b wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_83c8b6-8b"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-icon-hat kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewbox="0 0 1024 1024"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M796.672 99.942c-40.96-4.915-83.968-9.421-144.179-13.107 0 0 0 0 0 0-38.931-28.447-87.682-45.611-140.429-45.875l-0.064-0c-54.145 0.539-103.929 18.771-143.958 49.178l0.598-0.436c-1.719-0.499-3.693-0.786-5.734-0.786s-4.016 0.287-5.885 0.823l0.15-0.037-137.216 16.794c-100.629 13.139-177.716 97.727-178.994 200.573l-0.001 0.131c0.053 27.589 3.034 54.452 8.648 80.333l-0.456-2.509c12.516 55.745 57.68 98.149 113.943 106.406l0.745 0.090v471.040c0 11.311 9.169 20.48 20.48 20.48v0h655.36c11.311 0 20.48-9.169 20.48-20.48v0-471.040c57.008-8.347 102.172-50.751 114.515-105.579l0.173-0.917c5.215-23.8 8.202-51.139 8.202-79.175 0-0.965-0.004-1.93-0.011-2.894l0.001 0.148c-3.627-105.030-83.209-190.403-185.337-203.057l-1.031-0.104zM934.707 376.422c-10.524 42.853-48.611 74.143-94.005 74.143-0.359 0-0.718-0.002-1.077-0.006l0.055 0c-11.311 0-20.48 9.169-20.48 20.48v0 471.040h-614.4v-122.88h471.040c11.311 0 20.48-9.169 20.48-20.48s-9.169-20.48-20.48-20.48v0h-471.040v-307.2c0-11.311-9.169-20.48-20.48-20.48v0c-0.304 0.003-0.663 0.005-1.022 0.005-45.395 0-83.481-31.291-93.867-73.48l-0.138-0.663c-4.689-20.976-7.376-45.068-7.376-69.787 0-0.522 0.001-1.043 0.004-1.564l-0 0.080c2.285-81.399 63.601-147.8 142.539-158.019l0.821-0.087 96.256-13.107c-29.835 35.352-52.253 77.978-64.24 124.782l-0.476 2.194c-0.411 1.518-0.648 3.26-0.648 5.058 0 9.425 6.496 17.332 15.256 19.489l0.138 0.029c1.631 0.477 3.505 0.752 5.443 0.752 9.463 0 17.396-6.549 19.515-15.361l0.028-0.137c20.993-103.73 108.168-181.833 214.752-188.789l0.698-0.036c108.457 7.126 196.383 86.808 216.038 190.638l0.231 1.464c2.282 9.007 10.316 15.566 19.882 15.566 0.066 0 0.133-0 0.199-0.001l-0.010 0h4.915c8.925-2.34 15.402-10.334 15.402-19.841 0-1.829-0.24-3.601-0.689-5.288l0.032 0.143c-12.523-51.699-36.318-96.652-68.729-133.912l0.326 0.383c35.226 2.867 65.126 6.144 91.75 9.83 84.354 9.884 149.378 80.292 150.731 166.16l0.002 0.137c0 0.031 0 0.067 0 0.103 0 24.486-2.686 48.345-7.779 71.298l0.406-2.178z"/><path d="M297.37 429.67c-2.518-9.108-10.731-15.684-20.48-15.684-11.716 0-21.213 9.498-21.213 21.213 0 1.967 0.268 3.871 0.769 5.679l-0.035-0.149c14.198 51.705 39.581 96.325 73.505 132.914l-0.186-0.203c3.774 4.098 9.166 6.656 15.155 6.656 11.367 0 20.582-9.215 20.582-20.582 0-5.378-2.063-10.274-5.44-13.941l0.013 0.014c-29.087-31.798-50.832-70.807-62.242-114.015l-0.427-1.902z"/><path d="M752.845 409.6c-1.339-0.3-2.877-0.471-4.456-0.471-9.744 0-17.96 6.544-20.493 15.476l-0.036 0.15c-11.599 47.93-34.469 89.424-65.694 123.052l0.158-0.172c-3.719 3.646-6.024 8.722-6.024 14.336s2.305 10.69 6.021 14.333l0.003 0.003c3.747 3.508 8.783 5.679 14.325 5.734l0.011 0c6.466-0.237 12.107-3.562 15.521-8.535l0.043-0.067c35.676-38.281 62.071-85.68 75.31-138.306l0.466-2.187c0.156-0.959 0.245-2.065 0.245-3.192 0-9.584-6.454-17.661-15.253-20.12l-0.147-0.035z"/><path d="M512 409.6c-11.311 0-20.48 9.169-20.48 20.48v0 122.88c0 11.311 9.169 20.48 20.48 20.48s20.48-9.169 20.48-20.48v0-122.88c0-11.311-9.169-20.48-20.48-20.48v0z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">Chef's pro tip</span></h3>

<p class="kt-adv-heading12803_43fcef-d3 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_43fcef-d3">To ensure a perfect texture, thaw and drain your frozen spinach thoroughly. Squeeze out any excess moisture using a clean kitchen towel or strainer. Handle the delicate phyllo sheets carefully to avoid breaking them into smaller pieces. These simple steps will help you create a delicious and visually appealing pie.</p>

<h2 id="what-to-serve-with-spanakopita"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_583a54-4e wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_583a54-4e">What to serve with spanakopita?</h2>


<p>This <strong>Greek spinach and feta cheese pie</strong> can stand alone as a main dish. But pair it with some keto-friendly side dishes, and you get a delicious dinner.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_01750c-d2 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_d1d7ea-66"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Greek salad</strong>: Relish the Mediterranean flavors with a classic <a href="https://www.castironketo.net/blog/keto-greek-salad/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Greek Salad</a> for natural freshness.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_ab7b2d-f6"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Grilled chicken</strong>: Pair your Spanakopita with grilled chicken for a protein-packed meal.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_6eb54a-c7"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><a href="https://www.castironketo.net/blog/keto-tzatziki-sauce-recipe/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Keto Tzatziki Sauce</strong></a><strong>:</strong> Pair your spinach pie with a creamy Greek feta dip.</span></li></ul></div>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_8e0f44-81 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="801" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3.webp" alt="Fresh baked Spanakopita dish placed on kitchen table." class="kb-img wp-image-13245" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-360x240.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-768x513.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-720x481.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-180x120.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-3-150x100.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h2 id="how-to-make-it-healthier"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_5a36ed-6d wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_5a36ed-6d">How to make it healthier?</h2>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_5e1d10-de kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_5d3609-83"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Buy organic spinach and spring onions.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_f65677-bc"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">If you want a low-sodium option, reduce the amount of salt in the mix.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_62a213-86"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Add leafy greens like kale or Swiss chard to the spinach mixture for more fiber.</span></li></ul></div>


<h2 id="time-saving-tips"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_fcd515-04 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_fcd515-04">Time-saving tips</h2>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_a71c42-96 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_520976-4c"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Buy pre-washed spinach and save time on washing and drying.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_964297-96"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Freeze the feta cheese for about 15 minutes before you start cooking. It helps to crumble the cheese quickly.</span></li></ul></div>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_7a39d5-ab size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6.webp" alt="Greek spinach pie served on two plates from the baking dish." class="kb-img wp-image-13248" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-360x540.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-768x1152.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-720x1080.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-1024x1536.webp 1024w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-180x270.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-6-150x225.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h2 id="what-can-i-prepare-ahead-of-time"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_8841d8-15 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_8841d8-15">What can I prepare ahead of time?</h2>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_865326-f0 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_e1ebf1-f6"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Prepare the phyllo sheets in advance and store them in the refrigerator until you're ready to use them.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_121d6a-1b"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text">Make the spinach filling with raw spinach and cheese. Store it in the fridge until your dough is ready to assemble.</span></li></ul></div>


<h2 id="storage-and-reheating-instructions"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_4a4265-4c wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_4a4265-4c">Storage and reheating instructions</h2>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_7ec89e-6d wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_7ec89e-6d">Storage tips</h3>


<p>Spanakopita is best enjoyed the day it's made. But that doesn't mean you can't enjoy the leftovers. Here's how to store your spanakopita:</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_2ce4c4-cf kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_0f767c-89"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Refrigerator: </strong>Place the leftover spanakopita in an airtight container. It will keep for 2-3 days in the fridge.</span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_d20eb6-fe"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Freezer</strong>: If you plan to freeze this delicious meal, do it before baking. Wrap each square with plastic wrap and store them in a freezer-safe bag. They will keep for 2-3 months.</span></li></ul></div>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_61f8c7-0f size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8.webp" alt="Pieces of Greek spinach pie placed on parchment paper." class="kb-img wp-image-13250" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-360x540.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-768x1152.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-720x1080.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-1024x1536.webp 1024w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-180x270.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-8-150x225.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h3 class="kt-adv-heading12803_bf8e53-bc wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_bf8e53-bc">Reheating best practices</h3>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_2dae6d-ae kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_9e020b-63"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong>Oven</strong>: To reheat the refrigerated leftovers, place them in a baking dish and bake in a preheated oven at 375°F for 10 to 15 minutes. For the frozen ones, thaw them and bake them in a preheated oven at 355°F (180°C) for 25 minutes.</span></li></ul></div>


<h2 id="recipe-wrap-up-conclusion"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_313a50-be wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_313a50-be">Recipe wrap-up conclusion</h2>


<p>Indulge in this tasty <strong>Keto Spanakopita</strong>, where crunchy phyllo and creamy spinach filling blend just right. Picture it as a fancy supper or appetizer that'll please the whole gang at your next get-together. Relish this delectable Greek delight with no fret about extra carbs!</p>



<p>When you yearn for some soul-soothing grub, keep this beloved dish in mind and savor your meal. It's a recipe that'll satiate you without veering off your keto regimen. Now, let's get cookin'!</p>


<figure class="wp-block-kadence-image kb-image12803_d8b395-61 size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9.webp" alt="Slices of homemade Spanakopita recipe on parchment paper." class="kb-img wp-image-13251" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9.webp 1200w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-360x540.webp 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-768x1152.webp 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-720x1080.webp 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-1024x1536.webp 1024w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-180x270.webp 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-9-150x225.webp 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>

<h4 class="kt-adv-heading12803_f0e18a-10 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_f0e18a-10">Looking for more Greek dishes? Here are some keto-friendly options for you:</h4>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items12803_4d2696-c6 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone kt-list-icon-aligntop"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list"><li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_7ae88b-0a"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><a href="https://www.castironketo.net/blog/keto-moussaka/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Keto Moussaka</a></span></li>

