<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_c314df-0d"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><a href="https://www.castironketo.net/blog/keto-tzatziki-sauce-recipe/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Keto Tzatziki Sauce</a></span></li>

<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-12803_1622c7-ac"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fe_checkCircle kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><a href="https://www.castironketo.net/blog/mediterranean-keto-shrimp-zoodles/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mediterranean Keto Shrimp Zoodles</a></span></li></ul></div>


<h2 id="frequently-asked-questions"   class="kt-adv-heading12803_542099-fa wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_542099-fa">Frequently asked questions</h2>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-accordion alignnone"><div class="kt-accordion-wrap kt-accordion-id12803_d7202b-62 kt-accordion-has-11-panes kt-active-pane-0 kt-accordion-block kt-pane-header-alignment-left kt-accodion-icon-style-arrow kt-accodion-icon-side-right" style="max-width:none"><div class="kt-accordion-inner-wrap" data-allow-multiple-open="false" data-start-open="none">
<div class="wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-1 kt-pane12803_b272a5-12"><div class="kt-accordion-header-wrap"><button class="kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title"><strong><strong>Can I place the pan directly on the stove?</strong></strong></span></span><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger"></span></button></div><div class="kt-accordion-panel kt-accordion-panel-hidden"><div class="kt-accordion-panel-inner"><p class="kt-adv-heading12803_633203-f4 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_633203-f4">No, the double-boiling method is a must for this recipe. If you cook the phyllo directly over the stove, it will dry out and burn.</p></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-3 kt-pane12803_b488f7-d5"><div class="kt-accordion-header-wrap"><button class="kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title"><strong><strong>Does the pan need to be completely flat?</strong></strong></span></span><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger"></span></button></div><div class="kt-accordion-panel kt-accordion-panel-hidden"><div class="kt-accordion-panel-inner"><p class="kt-adv-heading12803_5a2f7c-f0 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_5a2f7c-f0">Yes, it does. Even a slight elevation in the center of the non-stick pan affects the phyllo dough. We used three different pans and confirmed the recipe works best with a flat-bottomed granite pan.</p></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-4 kt-pane12803_d3ae4d-dc"><div class="kt-accordion-header-wrap"><button class="kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title"><strong><strong>What can I do if my phyllo dough breaks or tears while cooking?</strong></strong></span></span><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger"></span></button></div><div class="kt-accordion-panel kt-accordion-panel-hidden"><div class="kt-accordion-panel-inner"><p class="kt-adv-heading12803_582fe9-55 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_582fe9-55">If the sheet breaks during cooking, patch it with extra batter. No one will notice a small tear or two when it's baked.</p></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-5 kt-pane12803_9d7055-51"><div class="kt-accordion-header-wrap"><button class="kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title"><strong><strong>I don't have xanthan gum. Can I still make this recipe?</strong></strong></span></span><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger"></span></button></div><div class="kt-accordion-panel kt-accordion-panel-hidden"><div class="kt-accordion-panel-inner"><p class="kt-adv-heading12803_ca4e6d-9f wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_ca4e6d-9f">If you don't have xanthan gum, use psyllium husk powder. The texture might be slightly different, but it will still give the sheets the necessary elasticity.</p></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-6 kt-pane12803_99215f-66"><div class="kt-accordion-header-wrap"><button class="kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap"><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-title"><strong><strong>How thick should be my phyllo batter?</strong></strong></span></span><span class="kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger"></span></button></div><div class="kt-accordion-panel kt-accordion-panel-hidden"><div class="kt-accordion-panel-inner"><p class="kt-adv-heading12803_03ec3b-73 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading12803_03ec3b-73">The batter should have the consistency of a thick beverage, not a smooth, thick batter. If it's thick as a crepe, add a tablespoon of water and mix well.</p></div></div></div>
</div></div></div>


<div id="recipe"></div><h2 id="%f0%9f%93%96-recipe"  >📖 Recipe</h2><div id="wprm-recipe-container-12809" class="wprm-recipe-container" data-recipe-id="12809" data-servings="4"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-template-cast-iron-keto-custom-recipe-card"><div class="wprm-recipe-image wprm-block-image-circle"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" style="border-width: 10px;border-style: double;border-color: #ffffff;" width="200" height="200" src="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-360x360.jpg" class="attachment-200x200 size-200x200" alt="Keto Spanakopita" srcset="https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-360x360.jpg 360w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-720x720.jpg 720w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-180x180.jpg 180w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-96x96.jpg 96w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.castironketo.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/keto-spanakopita-featured-image.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></div>
